@startuml
title <font size=12>Laporan Penjualan - Owner</font>

actor Owner
participant Browser
participant Controller
participant Database
participant View

Owner->Browser: Akses Laporan Penjualan
Browser->Controller: GET /pemilik/laporan-penjualan\n(dengan filter tanggal)
Controller->Database: Query Transaksi\nberdasarkan date range
Database->Controller: Return semua transaksi
Controller->Controller: Hitung total transaksi\ndan total penjualan
Controller->Controller: Group transaksi\nby date (harian)
Controller->Controller: Hitung rata-rata\nper hari
Controller->View: Pass data:\n- totalTransaksi\n- totalPenjualan\n- laporanHarian\n- rataRataPerHari
View->Browser: Tampilkan laporan penjualan\ndengan grafik dan tabel detail
Browser->Owner: Laporan siap dilihat

@enduml
